videos.description: Brandon Silvers finds Tevaris McCormick for a 10-yard touchdown to give the Trojans a 7-0 lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Troy's McCormick hauls in TD catch

videos.description: Cedarius Rookard interception of Texas State's Damian Williams sets up Troy in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Rookard's INT puts Troy in Texas State territory

videos.description: Sam Letton 11-yard touchdown reception off the Texas State turnover increases the lead to 14-0 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Letton TD cashes in for Troy

videos.description: Brandon Silvers finds Tray Eafford in the end zone for a long touchdown pass to extend Troy's lead 24-0 in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Troy's Silvers throws a 43-yard TD to Eafford

videos.description: Damian Williams' pass is intercepted by Jawon McDowell to stop the Bobcats' drive.
videos.headline: Texas State's Williams throws second INT of the game

videos.description: Brandon Silvers finds Clark Quisenberry, who makes the nice for a touchdown to extend Troy's lead to 31-0.
videos.headline: Quisenberry holds on to the ball for a Troy TD

videos.description: Jordan Chunn's 43-yard rushing touchdown pushes the Trojans' lead to 41-0.
videos.headline: Troy's Chunn shows off speed with 43-yard TD run

videos.description: Damian Williams delivers a 37-yard pass to Elijah King for a Texas State first down.
videos.headline: Williams' pass puts Texas State in red zone

videos.description: Damian Williams keeps the football and runs 3 yards to the end zone to score the Bobcats first touchdown of the game against Troy.
videos.headline: Williams' TD puts Texas State on the board

videos.description: Kaleb Barker finds Richard Hallman who takes it to the house for a touchdown to extend Troy's lead to 55-6 at the end of the third quarter.
videos.headline: Troy scores on 59-yard pitch and catch

videos.description: Anthony Smith coughs it up and Adrian Wesley picks it up and returns it 12 yards. On the ensuing drive, Troy would score a touchdown to extend their lead to 62-6.
videos.headline: Wesley scoops up Texas State's fumble
